*Bombu* je bačen na grad (A bomb was thrown at the city).
Mi ćemo postaviti *bombu* unutar zgrade (We will place a bomb inside the building).
On je kupio *bombu* da uništi most (He bought a bomb to destroy the bridge).
Oni su dobili *bombu* da unište rezervoar (They got a bomb to destroy the tank).
Oni su skrivali *bombu* u svojim torbama (They were hiding a bomb in their bags).
Policija je našla *bombu* u parku (The police found a bomb in the park).